{"data":[{"id":563757627,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":307595822,"title":"高中生对哥德巴赫猜想的证明有哪些错误？","question_type":"normal","created":1546272354,"updated_time":1546301579,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/307595822","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"b2f508e8f839b8870763f8085b1085fb","url_token":"zhang-han-yu-1","name":"Monsieur TRISTE","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-dd81ecb548dcbf39ff6fa286ad1cca05_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-dd81ecb548dcbf39ff6fa286ad1cca05_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/b2f508e8f839b8870763f8085b1085fb","user_type":"people","headline":"An irreducible gay","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":2721,"is_followed":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/563757627","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546273259,"updated_time":1546276463,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":4137,"comment_count":260,"is_sticky":false,"admin_closed_comment":false,"comment_permission":"all","can_comment":{"reason":"","status":true},"reshipment_settings":"allowed","content":"大家新年快乐啊～\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-01c5e9f3157fc384dc5902e772958f2a_b.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"600\" data-rawheight=\"85\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"600\" data-original=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-01c5e9f3157fc384dc5902e772958f2a_r.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/noscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,\u0026lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='600'%20height='85'\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/svg\u0026gt;\" data-rawwidth=\"600\" data-rawheight=\"85\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"600\" data-original=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-01c5e9f3157fc384dc5902e772958f2a_r.jpg\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-01c5e9f3157fc384dc5902e772958f2a_b.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e就算定义了“负质数”也是没什么问题的，毕竟这种临时扩充定义的事情在数学上并不少见…\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e问题出在第一页对于命题的理解上。\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e第一页第六行，欲证：\u003cbr\u003e若-1是素数，则对任意正整数n，2n属于A。\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e它考虑了这个命题的逆否命题：\u003cbr\u003e若存在正整数n_0，使得2n_0∉A，则-1不是负质数。\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e（这个逆否命题是没法证出来的，因为它的结论“-1不是负质数”与之前的假设“-1是负质数”矛盾。）\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e况且，它的证明方法是：\u003cbr\u003e仅考虑n_0=1，此时“若”2n_0=2属于A，则-1是质数。\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e这就是在瞎说了…\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-01c5e9f3157fc384dc5902e772958f2a_b.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"600\" data-rawheight=\"85\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"600\" data-original=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-01c5e9f3157fc384dc5902e772958f2a_r.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/noscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,\u0026lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='600'%20height='85'\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/svg\u0026gt;\" data-rawwidth=\"600\" data-rawheight=\"85\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"600\" data-original=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-01c5e9f3157fc384dc5902e772958f2a_r.jpg\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-01c5e9f3157fc384dc5902e772958f2a_b.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e最后改编一首小词：\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e西江月  \u003ca data-hash=\"7d2c586e48e601bc6d9f7bf481ffe7a7\" href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/people/7d2c586e48e601bc6d9f7bf481ffe7a7\" class=\"member_mention\" data-hovercard=\"p$b$7d2c586e48e601bc6d9f7bf481ffe7a7\"\u003e@证明\u003c/a\u003e \u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e质数“逐一判断”，\u003cbr\u003e实则“有借无还”，\u003cbr\u003e命题颠倒“真”推“伪”，\u003cbr\u003e“歌猜”易证不难。\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e若你歧途不返，\u003cbr\u003e成功注定无缘。\u003cbr\u003e勤学苦练多思考，\u003cbr\u003e方入数学之园。","editable_content":"","excerpt":"大家新年快乐啊～ 就算定义了“负质数”也是没什么问题的，毕竟这种临时扩充定义的事情在数学上并不少见… 问题出在第一页对于命题的理解上。 第一页第六行，欲证： 若-1是素数，则对任意正整数n，2n属于A。 它考虑了这个命题